title: Meine Liebe
description:
The main hero of the anime is Orpherus, a young man who believes in a country ruled by its people and whose sister was killed in an act of terrorism two years prior.[2] Orpherus, nicknamed Orphe, is surrounded by his friends and rivals and together they struggle to make their dream come true â€” being the kingâ€™s advisors.

The anime from Bee Train studio was directed by Koichi Mashimo and had Minako Shiba as the character designer. The first season of the anime was aired on the Animax network on November 2004 and the second season on January 2006
